{"tid":2057531,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【612 個被控暴動的人．3】電影學生憾未拍畢業作：或是 30 歲前最後香港作品","createTime":"2020-06-09T12:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T15:16:33.000Z","uid":240362,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ea54bfd421a53b89861711b05a6b102f363f62b8","tid":2057531,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T12:40:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/612-%E5%80%8B%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA-3-%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%86%BE%E6%9C%AA%E6%8B%8D%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E4%BD%9C-%E6%88%96%E6%98%AF-30-%E6%AD%B2%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F612-%25E5%2580%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BA%25BA-3-%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2586%25BE%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%258B%258D%25E7%2595%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%2598%25AF-30-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%2593%2581%2F&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=38600023\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F612-%25E5%2580%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BA%25BA-3-%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2586%25BE%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%258B%258D%25E7%2595%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%2598%25AF-30-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%2593%2581%2F&h=a5afbcde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/612-%E5%80%8B%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA-3-%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%86%BE%E6%9C%AA%E6%8B%8D%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E4%BD%9C-%E6%88%96%E6%98%AF-30-%E6%AD%B2%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81/</a><br />\n<br />\n抗爭一年，《立場新聞》訪問多個在反送中運動裡被控暴動的人，了解他們抗爭的初衷，記錄每一個「612 分之一」在此人生關口上的不安與期盼。<br />\n<br />\n今年三月，伊朗異見導演拉素羅夫 (Mohammad Rasoulof) 憑批判伊朗死刑制度的電影《There Is No Evil》，獲得第 70 屆柏林影展最高榮譽金熊獎。由於被伊朗政府限制出境，他未能親身赴柏林領獎，獲獎三天後，更收到入獄服刑通知 &mdash; 去年拉素羅夫被當局以「攻擊國家安全」罪名判處一年徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n被控暴動的電影系學生 Walter（化名）接受《立場新聞》訪問時，說起這個導演的故事。<br />\n<br />\n「以電影入罪」，或成明日香港寫照。可是還未到那天，Walter 也來不及擔心畢業作品的命運。最初他從沒想過以電影參與反送中運動，卻是被捕後的經歷，令他構思中的劇本變得完整。處子劇本開拍無期，他又即將迎來答辯，這份未完成的作品成為他的遺憾，「假設我要坐監，佢好可能係我 30 歲前最後一份香港作品。」"},{"pid":"703d53aaa5418f5b79f73c50e15534abc4b67818","tid":2057531,"uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T12:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7712e5d653ba5a5b7e927fdacca8232766b702b3","tid":2057531,"uid":229275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T12:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0918b7fe15fdb9d41c668f4e0870900eef9fc34c","tid":2057531,"uid":182827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T12:48:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c44096c7bb10f92565e869159789495473234f5","tid":2057531,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:46:49.000Z","msg":"會落雪嘅香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dedd0bb6b086b185b79a59feca68460d9838e78e","tid":2057531,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020